bck0186: COMPILES (Part07 verified). Added colimCompact infrastructure.

New module ColimCompactHelpers (parameterized by Sequence S'):
  - iterMap : iterate sequence map d times, obj S' n → obj S' (d + n)
  - inclIter : incl x ≡ incl (iterMap d x) via repeated push
  - liftTo : lift element to higher stage using n ≤ N
  - inclLift : incl x ≡ incl (liftTo le x) combining iterMap + J-based subst proof
  - inStage : every SeqColim element is merely at some stage

New functions:
  - colimCompactFin : Fin k → SeqColim S' factors through a stage (by induction on k)
  - colimCompact : A → SeqColim S' factors through a stage for any finite A

Building block for tex Lemma 1160 (ODiscColimOfODisc).
Uses max/left-≤-max/right-≤-max for combining stages in inductive step.
Note: right-≤-max has implicit order {n} {m} (swapped vs left-≤-max's {m} {n}).

